{"tid":825313,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"熊貓精靈","createTime":"2018-09-17T13:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T07:03:09.000Z","uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74d535614ef12090a34c779699f5b4ed62698993","tid":825313,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"4個月前買左兩條熊貓精靈同兩條白翅玫瑰加小小孔雀類魚養...<br />\n<br />\n大部份都死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家得返兩條熊貓同一條白翅..照計佢地其實好地地.同都算易養..但近一個月..有一條熊貓成日食好少野..又比其他兩條追...跟住佢就會哩埋係水底搵窿哩埋(之前D孔雀類又係咁一條條死左)....見佢越來越瘦.覺佢會好似之前D咁死...各位有無方法救救佢?<br />\n<br />\n利申一日喂一次..兩星期換水..有掛濾"},{"pid":"0c3e612d8e01c177e4a7186ab26d8b4191182efd","tid":825313,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fa31d7ba3b5235876cfca5179f1b7ae3da25c60","tid":825313,"uid":47099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"缸幾大？"},{"pid":"de6cfbec9b0c3d65458a5860c99be107092dbb20","tid":825313,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"餓就會食埋你啲孔雀魚架啦 怕咩<br />\n兩星期換水 未必好好"},{"pid":"ddcedb7602d7422915da78cae121715337c3e6b4","tid":825313,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fa31d7ba3b5235876cfca5179f1b7ae3da25c60","tid":825313,"uid":47099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"缸幾大？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"好細. 6,7吋"},{"pid":"90bacb238aca120fdf619c1f4730d464750c7a1b","tid":825313,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de6cfbec9b0c3d65458a5860c99be107092dbb20","tid":825313,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"餓就會食埋你啲孔雀魚架啦 怕咩<br />\n兩星期換水 未必好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"咁幾耐一次好，d燈會食孔雀？"},{"pid":"61dd4029d1bcc51ea8b499ac6dc0f9413c9fb4fa","tid":82531